<plot>In the film 'Just Like You', three child burn survivors share their stories in a way that helps the audience understand their challenges and accept their differences. This film is designed to prevent ostracism and to promote acceptance of child burn survivors...to reduce the emotional pain of kids who have already suffered so much.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?282326</url></doc>
